800&h=55db25cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Hh687ty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHh687ty.jpg&h=48f61840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCPU MTK 6737, Quad-core 1.3Ghz<br />\nRAM 2 GB<br />\n<br />\n&euro;139<br />\n<br />\nNokia 3310<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.contentful.com/wcfotm6rrl7u/6We1zbY7Mk8Mm0CQAyEmKy/dd2c9cf2667b2bda0c10ce7c9446faf5/Nokia-3310-Hero-Phone-V2.png?fm=png&amp;q=30&amp;w=800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.contentful.com%2Fwcfotm6rrl7u%2F6We1zbY7Mk8Mm0CQAyEmKy%2Fdd2c9cf2667b2bda0c10ce7c9446faf5%2FNokia-3310-Hero-Phone-V2.png%3Ffm%3Dpng%26q%3D30%26w%3D800&h=63d53227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/50clQNW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F50clQNW.png&h=dcd2faf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&euro;49"},{"pid":"8fd7ee6257561caa490594878f124a90d40695ff","tid":135943,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你老母<br />\n我真係好撚開心<br />\nNokia 既然有Android新機出<br />\n不過全部都係中低階機<br />\n不過算啦<br />\n我都明白呢個市場最多肉食<br />\n岩岩出返機<br />\n試下市場反應都好既<br />\n等其實廠出哂下一代旗艦機再出都未遲<br />\n<br />\n最撚開心既就係出返3310<br />\n嘩<br />\n真係聽到都興奮到3日3夜訓唔到<br />\n不過點撚解<br />\n你要設計到咁撚核突<br />\n原原本本咁咁好<br />\nD人鐘意3310都係買佢個情懷姐<br />\n你而家改到咁樣鬼5馬6<br />\n我都唔知點將新呢部3310同舊嗰部連結埋一齊<br />\n你而家改到咁撚樣<br />\n我買Nokia 150唔好<br />\n最後一句<br />\n屌你老母啦Nokia"},{"pid":"34eab9d1d8c2d2a43fceedd5b93d1714f29a1947","tid":135943,"uid":33463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"咪又係an機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b51b3dc12d7cd3459c2c8d174eeeab9a391d3bd","tid":135943,"uid":34178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"粒u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cd0cd4ad8f337f264396d46383945d5bdeb86c","tid":135943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20170226_event_nokia_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20170226_event_nokia_01.jpg&h=26faa596&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"981aaad5cbed2c992536994a175a767b0a9d0f7d","tid":135943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"千一買入手!  Nokia 智能手機三炮響！你搶唔搶？<br />\nKeith Paul Matt Yim(keithyim) 2017-02-26 23:15<br />\n<br />\nNokia 回歸手機市場，應係 2017 年機迷最關注的新聞。一來，Nokia 這個品牌出開的手機都有不錯的評價，二來，由以前 Nokia 公佈投入 Windows Phone 懷抱，到最後被 Microsoft 收購又遺棄，網友也想有朝一日，Nokia 會推出 Android 手機! 恨到了! 係 MWC2017 手機展裡，Nokia 一出三款 Android 智能手機，只可惜是，全部是低中檔配置！最平千一蚊入手，Nokia 品牌，唔難入口。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2017-02/26/207678/keithyim_1_c6d899f0ded50f0d73a7b07ca7eba26c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-02%2F26%2F207678%2Fkeithyim_1_c6d899f0ded50f0d73a7b07ca7eba26c.jpg&h=61ef7fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千一買入手!  Nokia 智能手機三炮響！你搶唔搶？<br />\n<br />\n三款中低檔<br />\nNokia 於 MWC2017 一口氣推出四款手機，其中一款是 Feature Phone，是復刻版 3310，ePrice 已有實機評測，大家可以 Click 這裡重温。另外三款都是 Android 智能手機。說三款，其實當中的 Nokia 6 早在中國大陸上市，香港亦有水貨好一段時間。雖然有一款是半新不舊，但肯定三款新機都有國際版。國際版  Nokia 手機有什麼好處？就是跟 BlackBerry 與 MOTO 一樣，會宗於 Android 的原生功能。而版主睇到 Nokia 三款手機，都是跟了 Android 7 版本，連 App Drawer 也是原生的，亦支援 Google Assistant，跟 Pixel 系列好似。"},{"pid":"fe855b297e3a2386c2110f15baf8ce92d1de7627","tid":135943,"uid":55847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"430<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收皮啦"}]}